&lt;p&gt;Pipe Layers are responsible for&amp;nbsp;installing pipe in storm sewers, gas utilities, and water mains. Laborers must have physical strength, endurance and must also be able to concentrate on their tasks. Assist Foreman and skilled craft workers in performing their assigned duties under close supervision&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Typical Duties:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Digging, spreading and leveling dirt, sand and gravel using a pick shovel or rake&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Installs, removes, and maintains a variety of erosion control products and liner. Clearing seditment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lift, carry and hold construction materials, tools and supplies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clean tools, equipment, material in work area&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mix, pour and spread concrete, asphalt, gravel and other materials using hand tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Positioning, cutting and fusing pipe&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Connecting various pipe pieces by glue, heat, or slip jointing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintaining depth by checking the laser beam or grade stakes and communicating with the operator&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cementing around pipes and inlets&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicating with the operator about the alignment of the pipe by using hand signals to ensure the proper depth&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inspecting the pipe fittings to ensure it is defect free and clean&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform a variety of machine tasks such as tapping soil, jackhammering and assisting in the fusing of pipe.&lt;/li&gt;
