&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate would have general experience in construction and project management with a high-level understanding of Oracle P6, contract requirements, and claim implications.&amp;nbsp; Candidate would be self-motivated with strong leadership and problem-solving skills in order to manage all schedule related matters and personnel.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will focus on our Mid-Atlantic Region (Baltimore and Virginia).&lt;/p&gt;
